``std/help``
 and used 
``is-not-empty``
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16245] added OSC 9;4 progress bar to std/bench
blindFS:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16376] fixed missing span for short flags requiring values
ItsHarper:
